  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >VINCENT'S EPIC ADVENTURE AWAITS YOU!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i>Map Of Materials</i>, Vincent finds himself stranded on a mysterious island. To escape and return to his old life, he must rely on his skills, his mind - and your courage. Will he make it out alive?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore dark ruins, face dangerous creatures, and discover useful items as you uncover the island’s secrets. Each area brings new challenges - from icy winter landscapes to ancient castle ruins and sand labyrinths. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809500/extras/d1af7d2e9f4565f5fd3c7b133678f708.avif?t=1770872630\" width=640 height=356 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >IT WON'T BE EASY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game won’t tell you where to go or what to do next. Vincent’s journey depends entirely on your problem-solving skills and player ability.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809500/extras/bd2662073a8f2cdb486330059a797ee0.avif?t=1770872630\" width=640 height=640 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809500/extras/dc472d56cbe04de036adb4fda50139d1.poster.avif?t=1770872630\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809500/extras/dc472d56cbe04de036adb4fda50139d1.webm?t=1770872630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809500/extras/dc472d56cbe04de036adb4fda50139d1.mp4?t=1770872630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore</strong> - Discover an Open World From a Third-Person View</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809500/extras/7ef4bfff3f59eb79c6ac45a32eabb5b4.poster.avif?t=1770872630\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809500/extras/7ef4bfff3f59eb79c6ac45a32eabb5b4.webm?t=1770872630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809500/extras/7ef4bfff3f59eb79c6ac45a32eabb5b4.mp4?t=1770872630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Terrain</strong> - Caves, Ruins, Tombs, Various Biomes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809500/extras/e0268d9d958b38c9cbefaefff0701889.poster.avif?t=1770872630\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809500/extras/e0268d9d958b38c9cbefaefff0701889.webm?t=1770872630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809500/extras/e0268d9d958b38c9cbefaefff0701889.mp4?t=1770872630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survive</strong> - To Survive, You'll Need to Ration Your Food</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809500/extras/9fcc5031565a22c532f7a3ff640519eb.poster.avif?t=1770872630\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/ste